      • blockContact

        int blockContact(java.lang.String address)
          throws android.os.RemoteException
        Blocks a contact. The ContactListListener will be notified when the contact is blocked successfully or any error occurs.
        Parameters:
        address - the address of the contact to block.
        Returns:
        ILLEGAL_CONTACT_LIST_MANAGER_STATE if contact lists is not loaded.
        Throws:
        android.os.RemoteException

      • unBlockContact
